originalText.text: The smartest, most caring psychiatrist with absolute integrity I've ever met or worked with.  After interviewing some 24 over the years I did the most intelligent thing in my life and that was becoming a year long patient of Dr. Trujillo's over a decade ago.  I've written seven books and sold over a million and one is dedicated to him.  He put everything in order for me and he did it quickly and without a lot on nonsense.  My marriage counselor even decided to go to him too after hearing what he did for me flying from LA to NY monthly to see him.  He made a great and positive difference in my life, un-complicating it.  I'll always be grateful to him and anyone lucky enough to get some of his time and thinking is most fortunate.
